      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Visual Conventions:\n\u2022 Rounded boxes = containers\n\u2022 Green = host / management\n\u2022 Purple = infrastructure\n\u2022 Yellow = CPE\n\u2022 Blue = client devices\n\u2022 Dashed bar = OVS bridge\n\nAll containers use\nnetwork_mode: none",
